<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV90">
<l>talaippeyti yāṉuṉ tiruvaṭic cūṭun takaimaiyiṉāl</l>
<l>nilaipeyta vākkaikku nōṟṟavim māyamu māyañcevvē</l>
<l>nilaippey tilāta nilaimaiyuṅ kāṇṭō ṟacurarkuḻān</l>
<l>tolaippeyta nēmiyen tāytollai yūḻi curuṅkalatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To attain  permanence by befitting conduct, meeting [you and]</l>
<l>wearing your holy feet [on my head], each time I see this marvel of my body</l>
<l>that did penance  and the state that does not marvellously attain permanence straight away,</l>
<l>o my father with the discus who brought ruin to a crowd of Asuras, the old aeon does not shrink.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
